column16: Marcus Semien flies out to right fielder Nomar Mazara.
Yonder Alonso doubles (29) on a sharp ground ball to right fielder Nomar Mazara.   Khris Davis scores.
Ryon Healy pops out to second baseman Rougned Odor.
Stephen Vogt flies out to left fielder Carlos Gomez.
Danny Valencia lines out to right fielder Nomar Mazara.
Joey Wendle lines out sharply to right fielder Nomar Mazara.
Brett Eibner pops out to shortstop Elvis Andrus.
Leonys Martin walks.   Dae-Ho Lee to 2nd.
Rangers challenged (tag play), call on the field was upheld: Dae-Ho Lee reaches on a fielder's choice, fielded by second baseman Rougned Odor.   Nelson Cruz scores.    Kyle Seager to 3rd.
Kyle Seager hits a ground-rule double (32) on a line drive to right field.   Nelson Cruz to 3rd.
Nelson Cruz singles on a line drive to left fielder Carlos Gomez.
Robinson Cano grounds out, second baseman Rougned Odor to first baseman Mitch Moreland.
Franklin Gutierrez singles on a ground ball to left fielder Carlos Gomez.   Ketel Marte scores.
Guillermo Heredia flies out to right fielder Nomar Mazara.
Ketel Marte grounds into a force out, third baseman Adrian Beltre to second baseman Rougned Odor.   Jesus Sucre out at 2nd.    Ketel Marte to 1st.
Jesus Sucre singles on a sharp line drive to center fielder Ian Desmond.
